                        <h6 class="text-uppercase fw-bold mb-4">
                            <i class="bi bi-gem me-3 text-secondary"></i>Company Name
                        </h6>
                        <p>Welcome to our Children's Toys Website - a place that provides high-quality products to help your little ones develop intellectually and create exciting play experiences. With a team of enthusiastic, professional and dedicated staff, we are committed to bringing you safe, diverse and suitable products for all ages and interests. Visit our website and explore the colorful world of children's toys today! </p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Grid column -->
                    <!-- Grid column -->
                    <div class="col-md-2 col-lg-2 col-xl-2 mx-auto mb-4">
